What seems like a pretty basic question actually has a lot of complexities. There are two ways to tackle onboarding: Product-led or sales-led. Which one is better? The most successful startups use product-led onboarding, but oftentimes the focus lies more on sales and the CACs. Sales often overshadow the efforts of the product team to drive key value. But why?

Check out the article to know more!
